<p style="font-size: 16px;">Hello <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>,</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px;">
  Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px;">
  You can unlock your account by clicking the button below:
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to 'Unlock My Account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token),
      style: "display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #0d6efd; color: #fff;
              text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;" %>
</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px;">
  If you did not attempt to sign in recently, please contact support for assistance.
</p>
